These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, peas, cherry, pepper
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | artichoke | peas | cherry | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, cola, mirinda
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | lemonade | mirinda | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, camping, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | camping | chess | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, scientific, sports
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | family | sports | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, baseball, skiing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | cycling | skiing | baseball | rowing |

