.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, spinach, tomato, peach
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating spinach is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | peach | spinach | nectarine | tomato |

