2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | snake | turtle | hedgehog | mouse |

